If I want to Thadoh Hatdo Gedo .. A fiery comment from Essam Urban to Gedo on his birthday
01 Nov 2019, 06:36 by Mustafa Karam
Mustafa Karam congratulated Essam El Hadary, former Egyptian team player, girlfriend of Mohamed Nagy Gedo, El Gouna player on his 35th birthday.Essam El Hadary tweeted on Twitter, saying: "Every year, you are good, darling. Ayez Thado Hatlo Gedo ". And received the tweet Essam Al-Hadary wide replies from follow-up via Twitter and the comments came between" every year and is good "and" every year and you are fine, Gedo and progress to progress, God willing, "and" dance dancing urban " ".
